{"tid":680171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家長secret: 教育局要開始普教幼/簡教中 了嗎？","createTime":"2018-05-27T04:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T00:24:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"327de69f3718c6aa97bafa418dae74da3bc0df75","tid":680171,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"內文較長，請各位家長耐心細讀<br />\n<br />\n教育局 提供以下課程<br />\n2018/07/23 (星期一) - 2018/08/01 (星期三)<br />\n<br />\n2018中小學及幼稚園教師普通話課程(幼稚園) <br />\n<br />\n活動目標<br />\n#鼓勵幼稚園教師持續進修，#提升普通話水平<br />\n<br />\n幼稚園教師 適用<br />\n<a href=\"https://tcs.edb.gov.hk/tcs/admin/courses/previewCourse/forPortal.htm?courseId=KGE020180060&amp;lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftcs.edb.gov.hk%2Ftcs%2Fadmin%2Fcourses%2FpreviewCourse%2FforPortal.htm%3FcourseId%3DKGE020180060%26lang%3Den&d=2vFTFNp9xPePz9ek5j2233Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=05b6f4e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tcs.edb.gov.hk/tcs/admin/courses/previewCourse/forPortal.htm?courseId=KGE020180060&amp;lang=en</a><br />\n<br />\n中小學及特殊學校 適用<br />\n<a href=\"https://tcs.edb.gov.hk/tcs/admin/courses/previewCourse/forPortal.htm?courseId=PDT020180099&amp;lang=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftcs.edb.gov.hk%2Ftcs%2Fadmin%2Fcourses%2FpreviewCourse%2FforPortal.htm%3FcourseId%3DPDT020180099%26lang%3Dzh&d=2vFTFNp9xPePz9ek5j2233Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=32c297f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tcs.edb.gov.hk/tcs/admin/courses/previewCourse/forPortal.htm?courseId=PDT020180099&amp;lang=zh</a><br />\n<br />\n#其一  此課程教授粤方言和普通話的關係<br />\n<br />\n在教育局的文件中 這個教師 持續進修 是有以下兩個進修講座。意味著，教育局鼓勵香港的幼稚園和中小學教師學習當中的知識和觀點，#並傳授給你和我的細路，或應用在教學之中。<br />\n<br />\n#粵方言與普通話的語音關係<br />\n第一堂 就是佢。真是好重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/248901/楊潤雄指「普教中」配套文件非近期上載\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F248901%2F%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E6%8C%87%E3%80%8C%E6%99%AE%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%8D%E9%85%8D%E5%A5%97%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%9D%9E%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89&d=2vFTFNp9xPePz9ek5j2233Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c16a118a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/248901/楊潤雄指「普教中」配套文件非近期上載</a>　僅提供/<br />\n<br />\n局長，宜家個課程 是2018年7月的，宜家5月，夠曬新鮮啦。<br />\n<br />\n#其二 教育局 有可能在掩蓋或誤導 課程內容<br />\n<br />\n各家長留意，幼稚園版本 和 中小學版本  第一堂 <br />\n<br />\n幼稚園版本<br />\n#粵方言與普通話的語音關係<br />\n<br />\n中小學版本<br />\n#粵語與普通話的語音關係<br />\n<br />\n由上堂時間表可知，兩個標題不同，並非 是兩個不同的講座，而是同一個講座。這裡絕對有理由懷疑，#粵方言與普通話的語音關係  才是將要教授的內容，但被更改標題，避免引起公關災難。<br />\n<br />\n咁你地明點解早前 教育局局長 唔知自己母語是咩？因為個課程2018年7月先開。佢未上堂。<br />\n<br />\n教育局改左中小學的嗰張的標題，天有眼，佢漏左改幼稚園嗰張的標題！<br />\n<br />\n《商品說明條例》(第362章) 涵蓋的範疇於二零一三年七月十九日全面執行，以禁止商戶對消費者作出某些不良營商手法，#包括就服務作出虛假商品說明、#誤導性遺漏、具威嚇性的營業行為、餌誘式廣告宣傳、先誘後轉銷售行為，以及不當地接受付款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.customs.gov.hk/tc/consumer_protection/trade_desc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.customs.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fconsumer_protection%2Ftrade_desc%2Findex.html&d=2vFTFNp9xPePz9ek5j2233Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=26bf732b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.customs.gov.hk/tc/consumer_protection/trade_desc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n#其三 <br />\n<br />\n#漢字簡化發展歷程，可能就是殘體字的演變過程。教育局這次不止是提供不同的學者意見，直情是灌輸殘體字的歷史和優點給香港的 幼稚園，小學 及中學 教師。<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記，這是一個教育局提供的教師進修課程。<br />\n<br />\n司馬昭之心，路人皆知！<br />\n<br />\n#其四 對比2017年的課程，可能已經 有向 教師灌輸 #粤方言 的做法，只是標題被改，隻字遮天，沒被發現。<br />\n<br />\n而且2017年，唯獨沒有 #漢字簡化發展歷程。 這是2018年新增的。用意何在，昭然若揭。<br />\n<br />\n最後一張， 教育局在2017年 修訂了 #幼稚園教育課程指引。當中 新舊版本 的改變，我們現在重溫一次，實在令人猜想漣漣。<br />\n<br />\n6月2日 就是小一派位放榜 叩門開始的大日子。<br />\n<br />\n@家長Secrets 只是希望各位家長在考慮入讀邊間小學時 把 #仍然堅持粤教中  這個優點放得前一些。<br />\n<br />\n因為，它們可能是最遲實行 #簡教中 的良心小學了。"},{"pid":"bd90a1c287097384fec48ea4c410aee04807c19e","tid":680171,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/122741_2d5e5b77591b69291c6557696592dcea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F122741_2d5e5b77591b69291c6557696592dcea.png&h=02c67ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/122749_730a8449c27384c68f5157def2a7b113.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F122749_730a8449c27384c68f5157def2a7b113.png&h=1df0ec91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/122750_655b9caca6282eb9da72efb1c3d5ce8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F122750_655b9caca6282eb9da72efb1c3d5ce8a.png&h=d518e4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/122751_c14a996250de037afa4d42c852c3ff4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F122751_c14a996250de037afa4d42c852c3ff4b.png&h=ea01db83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/122759_264e8e732d081173fa813255f92140a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F122759_264e8e732d081173fa813255f92140a2.png&h=6ba75b09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/122800_a0835a8730d371df4ddae6d187621685.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F122800_a0835a8730d371df4ddae6d187621685.png&h=5efb8526&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/122802_fa36c6c4fa6dd05881465e5984a3d06c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F122802_fa36c6c4fa6dd05881465e5984a3d06c.png&h=f29d1e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKParentsSecrets/posts/1963373473976613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKParentsSecrets%2Fposts%2F1963373473976613&d=2vFTFNp9xPePz9ek5j2233Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=15047df6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKParentsSecrets/posts/1963373473976613</a>"},{"pid":"bbcf3bea3b9c346cdd3f284b1e03d6c51d5e4036","tid":680171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8559b9ff0850bc38adf1e8ae4d1ef367a9372e13","tid":680171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75235de8cbc634ed3cc6ac12a0321d2a31f76017","tid":680171,"uid":53666,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"死返支那咪唔使咁煩囉"},{"pid":"88d65a5a2492651cf2ab41fe070be1d045ad49a4","tid":680171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"推，居然無人理"},{"pid":"c48601a2f966374989e8856fdd96e7c49cc99f42","tid":680171,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"做乜唔去大灣區教書"},{"pid":"7acd4cc48402d6fb333f81e797cdc1fc2f4059bc","tid":680171,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"572239ceb74e216483c8226383c3d0286a6c6041","tid":680171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6600eb248734f8a1b133f86a5a079f31779b04","tid":680171,"uid":70505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"本末倒置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812c6dd8f146b390e2285588f92260a3f30aea6e","tid":680171,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:3